item.description: Office Administrator Organization: The Lithuanian Cultural School of Chicago ¬∑ Part-time Duration: Apr 2018 - May 2020 (2 yrs 2 mos) Location: Chicago, Illinois, United States ¬∑ On-site I was an office admin and tech lead for a Lithuanian school on the south side of Chicago.
